::DevilDuer/Coput/Gawd-bot::

Coput's shuttle sinks into the ocean, leaving the side of the IRon Fist severely scraped. DevilDuer smashes into the side below the damage, rolling off and onto the ground, Coput landing hard behind him. DevilDuer jumps to his feet, kicking the unconcous Coput.

"Slag it!! Can't you watch where we're going???!!!!" he yells at the unresponding heap of stasis-locked circuits.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Gawd-bot sees the two pods crash, stopping his jumping and walking over to them.

"Hello, I'm the immortal Gawd-bot. What are your names?"



--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Abyssian Badass" <1641coburn@h...> wrote:
>     Two bots in pods crashed in the ocean by Alliance Island.  The two pods keep going down.  While going down, the DNA Scanners activate.  The first bot was a fuzor between a lobster and a sting ray.  The second bot also became a fuzor, of a shark and a seagull.  Just before the two pods hit the ocean floor, the two bots came came out from their pods.  They both transformed to beast mode, and surfaced.  The second bot, who had seagull wings, flew up from the ocean and was flying in the air.  The first bot came up too and swam to the shore of Alliance Island, and sat there.  The second bot followed.
> 
>     "Finally," the first bot shouted, "We've made it to planet Earth!  Let's find a good faction to join Anthrostite."

>     "Yes, I agree, Protostite," replied Anthrostite.
